.rule_6_6_8_ensure_login_message_is_set

Reference: Juniper Networks
(https://www.juniper.net/techpubs/software/junos/junos93/swconfig-system-
basics/configuring-a-system-login-message.html#id-10963857)
Agency (NSA)

Remediation: Configure a login message using the following command under the [edit system]
hierarchy:
[edit system]
user@host#set login message "<LEGAL NOTICE>"

